{"tid":1165354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人做咩事都好不安","createTime":"2019-05-21T17:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T11:31:03.000Z","uid":131492,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"402d551298cc864a0d8d9ed555382e3b4a393823","tid":1165354,"uid":131492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:39:32.000Z","msg":"做大事小事都好成日處於極不安狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好辛苦每做一件事之後會係個心只少loop十次先<br />\n但唔代表loop完就無咁緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好辛苦生活所有事都好焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想放鬆d但我完全放鬆唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775d52f7f7537cae1a1507b571a00112c7254d30","tid":1165354,"uid":239384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"做一件事之前成日要係個腦度預演幾次 做完又會成日係咁loop自己會唔會做得唔好 算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c31d6cacc11b2650feacb37d5621748721e9e92","tid":1165354,"uid":131492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"775d52f7f7537cae1a1507b571a00112c7254d30","tid":1165354,"uid":239384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"做一件事之前成日要係個腦度預演幾次 做完又會成日係咁loop自己會唔會做得唔好 算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T17:59:19.000Z","msg":"我就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得好困擾<br />\n生活上唔同大大小小既事都會令我好緊張<br />\n搞到根本每日都係緊張同不安之下渡過<br />\n由細到大都係易緊張既人<br />\n但人越大情況越嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連同陌生人講句野都會緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好影響每日生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7496b8447dd7fdbe50ae984ba4a9ede06088d3","tid":1165354,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike